<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Document</title>

    <style>
        input[type="range"] {
            width: 300px;
        }

        datalist {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            padding: 0 10px;
        }
      </style>
</head>
<body>
    <form form action="/submitSurvey" method="POST">
        <fieldset>
            <legend>Social Media Survey</legend>
            <br>
            <label for="location">Location</label>
            <select id="location" name="location">
                <option value="Provo" selected>Provo</option>
            </select>
            <br><br>
            <label for="numAge">What is your age? </label>
            <input type="number" id="numAge" name="age" min="1">
            <br><br>
            <label for="txtGender">Gender</label>
            <select id="txtGender" name="gender">
                <option value="" disabled selected style="color:grey;">select gender</option>
                <option value="Male">Male</option>
                <option value="Female">Female</option>
                <option value="Other">Other</option>
            </select>
            <br><br>
            <label for="rStatus">Relationship Status</label>
            <select id="rStatus" name="relationship">
                <option value="" disabled selected>select relationship status</option>
                <option value="In a relationship">In a relationship</option>
                <option value="Single">Single</option>
                <option value="Married">Married</option>
                <option value="Divorced">Divorced</option>
            </select>
            <br><br>
            <label for="oStatus">Occupation Status</label>
            <select id="oStatus" name="occupation">
                <option value="" disabled selected>select occupation</option>
                <option value="University Student">University Student</option>
                <option value="School Student">School Student</option>
                <option value="Salaried Worker">Salaried Worker</option>
                <option value="Retired">Retired</option>
            </select>
            <br><br>
            <label>What type of organizations are you affiliated with? (select all that apply)</label>
                <form>
                    <br>
                    <input type="checkbox" id="cbUni" name="organization_name" value="University">
                    <label>University</label>
                    <br>
                    <input type="checkbox" id="cbPrivate" name="organization_name" value="Private">
                    <label>Private</label>
                    <br>
                    <input type="checkbox" id="cbSchool" name="organization_name" value="School">
                    <label>School</label>
                    <br>
                    <input type="checkbox" id="cbCompany" name="organization_name" value="Company">
                    <label>Company</label>
                    <br>
                    <input type="checkbox" id="cbGovernment" name="organization_name" value="Government">
                    <label>Government</label>
                    <br>
                    <input type="checkbox" id="cbNone" name="organization_name" value="N/A">
                    <label>N/A</label>
                </form>
            <br><br>
            <label name="platform_name">Do you use social media?</label>
            <form>
                <input type="radio" id="rbUseSM" name="use_sm" value="Yes">
                <label for="rbUseSM">Yes</label>
                <br>
                <input type="radio" id="rbNotUse" name="use_sm" value="No">
                <label for="rbNotUse">No</label>
            </form>
            <br><br>
            <label>What social media platforms do you commonly use?</label>
            <br><br>
            <label>What is the average time you spend on social media every day?</label>
            <select id="avgTime" name="avg_daily_sm_use">
                <option value="" disabled selected>select time spent</option>
                <option value="Less than an Hour">Less than an Hour</option>
                <option value="Between 1 and 2 hours">Between 1 and 2 hours</option>
                <option value="Between 2 and 3 hours">Between 2 and 3 hours</option>
                <option value="Between 3 and 4 hours">Between 3 and 4 hours</option>
                <option value="Between 4 and 5 hours">Between 4 and 5 hours</option>
                <option value="More than 5 hours">More than 5 hours</option>
            </select>
            <br><br>
            <label>How often do you find yourself using social media without a specific purpose?</label>
            <br><br>
            <div style="text-align:left ; max-width: 400px; margin: 10;">
                <div style="display: flex; justify-content: space-between; margin-bottom: 10px;">
                    <span>Not Often</span>
                    <span>Very Often</span>
                </div>
                <div style="display: flex; justify-content: space-between; margin-bottom: 10px;">
                    <label style="flex: 1; text-align: center;">
                        <input type="radio" name="no_purpose_use_score" id="purposeUse1" value="1">1
                    </label>
                    <label style="flex: 1; text-align: center;">
                        <input type="radio" name="no_purpose_use_score" id="purposeUse2" value="2">2
                    </label>
                    <label style="flex: 1; text-align: center;">
                        <input type="radio" name="no_purpose_use_score" id="purposeUse3" value="3">3
                    </label>
                    <label style="flex: 1; text-align: center;">
                        <input type="radio" name="no_purpose_use_score" id="purposeUse4" value="4">4
                    </label>
                    <label style="flex: 1; text-align: center;">
                        <input type="radio" name="no_purpose_use_score" id="purposeUse5" value="5">5
                    </label>
                </div>
            </div>
            
            <br>
            <label>How often do you get distracted by social media when you are busy doing something?</label>
            <br><br>
            <div style="text-align:left ; max-width: 400px; margin: 10;">
                <div style="display: flex; justify-content: space-between; margin-bottom: 10px;">
                    <span>Not Often</span>
                    <span>Very Often</span>
                </div>
                <div style="display: flex; justify-content: space-between; margin-bottom: 10px;">
                    <label style="flex: 1; text-align: center;">
                        <input type="radio" name="distracted_use_score" id="distractScale1" value="1">1
                    </label>
                    <label style="flex: 1; text-align: center;">
                        <input type="radio" name="distracted_use_score" id="distractScale2" value="2">2
                    </label>
                    <label style="flex: 1; text-align: center;">
                        <input type="radio" name="distracted_use_score" id="distractScale3" value="3">3
                    </label>
                    <label style="flex: 1; text-align: center;">
                        <input type="radio" name="distracted_use_score" id="distractScale4" value="4">4
                    </label>
                    <label style="flex: 1; text-align: center;">
                        <input type="radio" name="distracted_use_score" id="distractScale5" value="5">5
                    </label>
                </div>
            </div>            
            <br><br>
            <label>Do you feel restless if you haven't used social media in a while?</label>
            <br>
            <div style="text-align:left ; max-width: 400px; margin: 10;">
                <div style="display: flex; justify-content: space-between; margin-bottom: 10px;">
                    <span>Not Often</span>
                    <span>Very Often</span>
                </div>
                <div style="display: flex; justify-content: space-between; margin-bottom: 10px;">
                    <label style="flex: 1; text-align: center;">
                        <input type="radio" name="restlessness_without_sm_score" id="restlessScale1" value="1">1
                    </label>
                    <label style="flex: 1; text-align: center;">
                        <input type="radio" name="restlessness_without_sm_score" id="restlessScale2" value="2">2
                    </label>
                    <label style="flex: 1; text-align: center;">
                        <input type="radio" name="restlessness_without_sm_score" id="restlessScale3" value="3">3
                    </label>
                    <label style="flex: 1; text-align: center;">
                        <input type="radio" name="restlessness_without_sm_score" id="restlessScale4" value="4">4
                    </label>
                    <label style="flex: 1; text-align: center;">
                        <input type="radio" name="restlessness_without_sm_score" id="restlessScale5" value="5">5
                    </label>
                </div>
            </div>            
            <br><br>
            <label>On a scale of 1 to 5, how easily distracted are you?</label>
            <br>
            <div style="text-align:left ; max-width: 400px; margin: 10;">
                <div style="display: flex; justify-content: space-between; margin-bottom: 10px;">
                    <span>Not Distracted</span>
                    <span>Easily Distracted</span>
                </div>
                <div style="display: flex; justify-content: space-between; margin-bottom: 10px;">
                    <label style="flex: 1; text-align: center;">
                        <input type="radio" name="general_distraction_score" id="ezdistScale1" value="1">1
                    </label>
                    <label style="flex: 1; text-align: center;">
                        <input type="radio" name="general_distraction_score" id="ezdistScale2" value="2">2
                    </label>
                    <label style="flex: 1; text-align: center;">
                        <input type="radio" name="general_distraction_score" id="ezdistScale3" value="3">3
                    </label>
                    <label style="flex: 1; text-align: center;">
                        <input type="radio" name="general_distraction_score" id="ezdistScale4" value="4">4
                    </label>
                    <label style="flex: 1; text-align: center;">
                        <input type="radio" name="general_distraction_score" id="ezdistScale5" value="5">5
                    </label>
                </div>
            </div>             
            <br><br>
            <label>On a scale of 1 to 5, how much are you bothered by worries?</label>
            <br>
            <div style="text-align:left ; max-width: 400px; margin: 10;">
                <div style="display: flex; justify-content: space-between; margin-bottom: 10px;">
                    <span>Not Bothered</span>
                    <span>Very Bothered</span>
                </div>
                <div style="display: flex; justify-content: space-between; margin-bottom: 10px;">
                    <label style="flex: 1; text-align: center;">
                        <input type="radio" name="bothered_by_worries_score" id="botheredScale1" value="1">1
                    </label>
                    <label style="flex: 1; text-align: center;">
                        <input type="radio" name="bothered_by_worries_score" id="botheredScale2" value="2">2
                    </label>
                    <label style="flex: 1; text-align: center;">
                        <input type="radio" name="bothered_by_worries_score" id="botheredScale3" value="3">3
                    </label>
                    <label style="flex: 1; text-align: center;">
                        <input type="radio" name="bothered_by_worries_score" id="botheredScale4" value="4">4
                    </label>
                    <label style="flex: 1; text-align: center;">
                        <input type="radio" name="bothered_by_worries_score" id="botheredScale5" value="5">5
                    </label>
                </div>
            </div>             
            <br><br>
            <label>Do you find it difficult to concentrate on things?</label>
            <br>
            <div style="text-align:left ; max-width: 400px; margin: 10;">
                <div style="display: flex; justify-content: space-between; margin-bottom: 10px;">
                    <span>Very Easy</span>
                    <span>Very Difficult</span>
                </div>
                <div style="display: flex; justify-content: space-between; margin-bottom: 10px;">
                    <label style="flex: 1; text-align: center;">
                        <input type="radio" name="concentration_difficulty_score" id="concentrateScale1" value="1">1
                    </label>
                    <label style="flex: 1; text-align: center;">
                        <input type="radio" name="concentration_difficulty_score" id="concentrateScale2" value="2">2
                    </label>
                    <label style="flex: 1; text-align: center;">
                        <input type="radio" name="concentration_difficulty_score" id="concentrateScale3" value="3">3
                    </label>
                    <label style="flex: 1; text-align: center;">
                        <input type="radio" name="concentration_difficulty_score" id="concentrateScale4" value="4">4
                    </label>
                    <label style="flex: 1; text-align: center;">
                        <input type="radio" name="concentration_difficulty_score" id="concentrateScale5" value="5">5
                    </label>
                </div>
            </div>            
            <br><br>
            <label >On a scale of 1-5, how often do you compare yourself to other successful people through the use of social media?</label>
            <br><br>
            <div style="text-align:left ; max-width: 400px; margin: 10;">
                <div style="display: flex; justify-content: space-between; margin-bottom: 10px;">
                    <span>Not Often</span>
                    <span>Very Often</span>
                </div>
                <div style="display: flex; justify-content: space-between; margin-bottom: 10px;">
                    <label style="flex: 1; text-align: center;">
                        <input type="radio" name="freq_comparison_to_successful_people_via_sm_score" id="compareScale1" value="1">1
                    </label>
                    <label style="flex: 1; text-align: center;">
                        <input type="radio" name="freq_comparison_to_successful_people_via_sm_score" id="compareScale2" value="2">2
                    </label>
                    <label style="flex: 1; text-align: center;">
                        <input type="radio" name="freq_comparison_to_successful_people_via_sm_score" id="compareScale3" value="3">3
                    </label>
                    <label style="flex: 1; text-align: center;">
                        <input type="radio" name="freq_comparison_to_successful_people_via_sm_score" id="compareScale4" value="4">4
                    </label>
                    <label style="flex: 1; text-align: center;">
                        <input type="radio" name="freq_comparison_to_successful_people_via_sm_score" id="compareScale5" value="5">5
                    </label>
                </div>
            </div>
            <br><br>
            <label>Following the previous question, how do you feel about these comparisons, generally speaking?</label>
            <br><br>
            <div style="text-align:left ; max-width: 400px; margin: 10;">
                <div style="display: flex; justify-content: space-between; margin-bottom: 10px;">
                    <span>Very Bad</span>
                    <span>Very Good</span>
                </div>
                <div style="display: flex; justify-content: space-between; margin-bottom: 10px;">
                    <label style="flex: 1; text-align: center;">
                        <input type="radio" name="feelings_about_comparison_score" id="feelcompScale1" value="1">1
                    </label>
                    <label style="flex: 1; text-align: center;">
                        <input type="radio" name="feelings_about_comparison_score" id="feelcompScale2" value="2">2
                    </label>
                    <label style="flex: 1; text-align: center;">
                        <input type="radio" name="feelings_about_comparison_score" id="feelcompScale3" value="3">3
                    </label>
                    <label style="flex: 1; text-align: center;">
                        <input type="radio" name="feelings_about_comparison_score" id="feelcompScale4" value="4">4
                    </label>
                    <label style="flex: 1; text-align: center;">
                        <input type="radio" name="feelings_about_comparison_score" id="feelcompScale5" value="5">5
                    </label>
                </div>
            </div>
            <br><br>
            <label>How often do you look to seek validation from features of social media?</label>
            <br>
            <div style="text-align:left ; max-width: 400px; margin: 10;">
                <div style="display: flex; justify-content: space-between; margin-bottom: 10px;">
                    <span>Not Often</span>
                    <span>Very Often</span>
                </div>
                <div style="display: flex; justify-content: space-between; margin-bottom: 10px;">
                    <label style="flex: 1; text-align: center;">
                        <input type="radio" name="validation_seeking_from_sm_score" id="validScale1" value="1">1
                    </label>
                    <label style="flex: 1; text-align: center;">
                        <input type="radio" name="validation_seeking_from_sm_score" id="validScale2" value="2">2
                    </label>
                    <label style="flex: 1; text-align: center;">
                        <input type="radio" name="validation_seeking_from_sm_score" id="validScale3" value="3">3
                    </label>
                    <label style="flex: 1; text-align: center;">
                        <input type="radio" name="validation_seeking_from_sm_score" id="validScale4" value="4">4
                    </label>
                    <label style="flex: 1; text-align: center;">
                        <input type="radio" name="validation_seeking_from_sm_score" id="validScale5" value="5">5
                    </label>
                </div>
            </div>            
            <br><br>
            <label>How often do you feel depressed or down?</label>
            <br>
            <div style="text-align:left ; max-width: 400px; margin: 10;">
                <div style="display: flex; justify-content: space-between; margin-bottom: 10px;">
                    <span>Not Often</span>
                    <span>Very Often</span>
                </div>
                <div style="display: flex; justify-content: space-between; margin-bottom: 10px;">
                    <label style="flex: 1; text-align: center;">
                        <input type="radio" name="freq_feeling_depressed_or_down_score" id="depressedScale1" value="1">1
                    </label>
                    <label style="flex: 1; text-align: center;">
                        <input type="radio" name="freq_feeling_depressed_or_down_score" id="depressedScale2" value="2">2
                    </label>
                    <label style="flex: 1; text-align: center;">
                        <input type="radio" name="freq_feeling_depressed_or_down_score" id="depressedScale3" value="3">3
                    </label>
                    <label style="flex: 1; text-align: center;">
                        <input type="radio" name="freq_feeling_depressed_or_down_score" id="depressedScale4" value="4">4
                    </label>
                    <label style="flex: 1; text-align: center;">
                        <input type="radio" name="freq_feeling_depressed_or_down_score" id="depressedScale5" value="5">5
                    </label>
                </div>
            </div>                        
            <br><br>
            <label>On a scale of 1 to 5, how frequently does your interest in daily activities fluctuate?</label>
            <br>
            <div style="text-align:left ; max-width: 400px; margin: 10;">
                <div style="display: flex; justify-content: space-between; margin-bottom: 10px;">
                    <span>Not Often</span>
                    <span>Very Often</span>
                </div>
                <div style="display: flex; justify-content: space-between; margin-bottom: 10px;">
                    <label style="flex: 1; text-align: center;">
                        <input type="radio" name="freq_fluctuation_of_interest_in_daily_activities_score" id="interestScale1" value="1">1
                    </label>
                    <label style="flex: 1; text-align: center;">
                        <input type="radio" name="freq_fluctuation_of_interest_in_daily_activities_score" id="interestScale2" value="2">2
                    </label>
                    <label style="flex: 1; text-align: center;">
                        <input type="radio" name="freq_fluctuation_of_interest_in_daily_activities_score" id="interestScale3" value="3">3
                    </label>
                    <label style="flex: 1; text-align: center;">
                        <input type="radio" name="freq_fluctuation_of_interest_in_daily_activities_score" id="interestScale4" value="4">4
                    </label>
                    <label style="flex: 1; text-align: center;">
                        <input type="radio" name="freq_fluctuation_of_interest_in_daily_activities_score" id="interestScale5" value="5">5
                    </label>
                </div>
            </div>            
            <br><br>
            <label>On a scale of 1 to 5, how often do you face issues regarding sleep?</label>
            <br>
            <div style="text-align:left ; max-width: 400px; margin: 10;">
                <div style="display: flex; justify-content: space-between; margin-bottom: 10px;">
                    <span>Not Often</span>
                    <span>Very Often</span>
                </div>
                <div style="display: flex; justify-content: space-between; margin-bottom: 10px;">
                    <label style="flex: 1; text-align: center;">
                        <input type="radio" name="freq_sleep_issues_score" id="sleepScale1" value="1">1
                    </label>
                    <label style="flex: 1; text-align: center;">
                        <input type="radio" name="freq_sleep_issues_score" id="sleepScale2" value="2">2
                    </label>
                    <label style="flex: 1; text-align: center;">
                        <input type="radio" name="freq_sleep_issues_score" id="sleepScale3" value="3">3
                    </label>
                    <label style="flex: 1; text-align: center;">
                        <input type="radio" name="freq_sleep_issues_score" id="sleepScale4" value="4">4
                    </label>
                    <label style="flex: 1; text-align: center;">
                        <input type="radio" name="freq_sleep_issues_score" id="sleepScale5" value="5">5
                    </label>
                </div>
            </div> 

            <button type="submit">Submit</button>
        </fieldset>
    </form>
    
</body>
</html>